(firstQuint)Dexmedetomidine to Improve Outcomes During Emergence From Retroperitoneal Laparoscopic Surgery.

 Agitation during emergence is frequent after retroperitoneal urologic surgery.

 Dexmedetomidine is alpha-2 receptor agonist which shows sedative and algesic effect.

 In this study we will compare the effect of dexmedetomidine given by different protocols on emergence agitation.

